The aim in my writing for Jet is to create meaningful, helpful copy that informs, inspires and, most importantly, helps closes sales. I use a friendly voice to encourage engagement, while providing informative descriptions of products using feature/benefit structures. Product specifications are included as applicable, as are explanations of relevant technologies. All of this is done while keeping the copy SEO-friendly and adhering to strict word count limits.
